basic.Source: Synthetic construct(derived from the Membrane-Proximal Ectodomain of Feline Immunodeficiency Virus)
basic.Target Organism: [Ref.12610147]FIV-M2(Feline immunodeficiency virus M2):inhibition of virus replication in MBM cells(IC50=0.03 µg/ml);FIV-Pet(Feline immunodeficiency virus Pet):inhibition of virus replication in MBM cells(IC50=0.04 µg/ml).
